Package: ipl
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Swaha", "Bhattacharya", , "itsswahabhattacharya@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: 
    This package has data on IPL all IPL matches played in the years 2008-2020. 
    It contains functions to calculate the batting average, maximum runs made, strike rate, 
    and the number of centuriesand half-centuries made by a batsman in a given IPL season.
